erent parts of the world. Phones can now act as point-of-sale systems helping companies manage cash flow better. Automated payment technologies removed tedious tasks involved when handling money manually.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-it-helps-in-money-transfer\"><\/span>3. It Helps in Money Transfer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Small businesses that operate internationally can use Verv to facilitate international payments. It also allows the opening of multiple currency accounts that accept different currencies. These functions help firms to cut down transaction fees.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since Verv is responsible for international payments, it has a secure channel that secures clients&#8217; data and follows the legal regulations that keep clients&#8217; money safe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-provide-loans-and-other-forms-of-financial-services\"><\/span>4. Provide Loans and Other Forms of Financial Services<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting a loan from a traditional bank can be stressful. It requires many processes and paperwork before your loan is approved. However, with the emergence of fintech companies, entrepreneurs have access to quick loans that require fewer approval processes. Business people can acquire loans from Verv. Verv provides funds and other financial support to loyal customers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Verv, you can apply for a loan directly from your phone. The approval process takes less than 10 minutes. Verv offers loans that can assist in improving customer experience. This model helps businesses provide clients with services such as buy now and pay later. Verv also includes funding options for first-time entrepreneurs and small companies, such as crowdfunding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-improve-customer-insights-and-engagement\"><\/span>5. Improve Customer Insights and Engagement<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"